                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10122" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OB-0447</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">315 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人才梯队何以活力不息？潍柴技术研发人员的分层 激励之道</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Weichai: How Can Talent Lead Innovation? The Precision Incentive Approach for Weichai&#39;s R&amp;D Personnel</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘光建，苏畅，牟金铭，李思雨，司李一诺，蔡地（通讯作者），武常岐</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山东大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">潍柴控股集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">研发部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">潍柴；研发人员；职业生命周期；激励；国企专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">How Does the Talent Ladder Remain Dynamic? The Tiered  Incentive Approach for Weichai’s R&amp;D Personnel</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人才引领创新，如何对研发人员实施分层激励以推动创新是企业需要关
注的重要问题。面临企业进入“科技无人区”和行业转型的加速，潍柴构建了
聚焦研发人员的分层激励体系，针对其不同职业发展阶段的需求实施差异化的
激励措施。针对技术新人，潍柴通过“3+1”培训项目、“师徒制”和“新秀
奖”等措施，帮助其快速成长并建立职业自信。对于技术骨干，潍柴通过设立
高挑战项目、提供资源支持和荣誉激励，激发其内在成就动机。对于资深技术
专家，潍柴赋予其荣誉职位、提升决策话语权和认可其传承价值，推动达成从
个人成就到组织传承的有机衔接。本案例描述了潍柴不同阶段研发人员的差异
化需求、实施的针对性激励措施以及在 00 后研发人员加速涌入背景下将会面临
的挑战。本案例全面展示了潍柴围绕“分层次激励研发人员”所进行的一系列
探索和实践。这些探索和实践，具有很高的案例研讨价值，对于其他企业，尤
其是国有企业，亦具有重要的借鉴价值和启发意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Talent leads innovation, and how to implement tiered incentives for R&amp;D 
personnel to drive innovation is an important issue that enterprises need to focus on. 
Faced with the acceleration of enterprises entering the “technological no man’s land”
and industry transformation, Weichai has built a tiered incentive system focused on 
R&amp;D personnel, implementing differentiated incentive measures tailored to their needs 
at different career development stages.For technical newcomers, Weichai employs 
measures such as the “3+1” training program, a “mentorship system”, and the “Rising 
Star Award” to help them grow rapidly and build professional confidence. For technical 
backbone personnel, Weichai stimulates their intrinsic achievement motivation by 
setting high-challenge projects, providing resource support, and offering honorary 
incentives. For senior technical experts, Weichai grants them honorary positions, 
enhances their decision-making voice, and recognizes their legacy value, promoting an 
organic connection from personal achievement to organizational inheritance. This case 
describes the differentiated needs of Weichai’s R&amp;D personnel at different stages, the 
targeted incentive measures implemented, and the challenges that will arise in the 
context of the accelerating influx of post-00s R&amp;D personnel. This case 
comprehensively showcases a series of explorations and practices conducted by 
Weichai around the “tiered incentives of R&amp;D personnel”. These explorations and 
practices hold significant value for case study and discussion, and also offer important 
reference and inspirational significance for other enterprises, especially state-owned 
enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《组织行为学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">职业生命周期理论；马斯洛需求层次理论；主动性动机模型</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-11</td>
                            </tr>
